Open source code repositories used for mod:
Lambda Fortress: (The original Lambda Fortress source code) https://github.com/Benoist3012/TF2HLCoop
Team Fortress 2 Classic: (Base code) https://github.com/mastercoms/TF2Classic
Half-Life 2 Community Edition: (Discord RPC, sound timescale) https://gitlab.com/RaraCerberus/HL2CE
Team Fortress 2 Vintage: (Custom weapons and improvements) https://github.com/bachingo/TF2Vintage
Petercov's Source++: (NAV NPCs support and Squad System ) https://github.com/Petercov/Source-PlusPlus
SMOD13: (Animation fix for hl2/ep1/ep2 maps) https://gitlab.com/RaraCerberus/SMOD13
Opposing force 2: (Combine Synth model and csmg1 weapon): https://github.com/of2team/Opposing-Force-2   

Community Contributors: 
